            I selected the <a href="https://www.dinesen.com/en/products/dinesen-collection/table/">Dinesen</a> as my reference design because it was both beautiful, and relatively simple in construction. I love how it elegantly creates visual interest from relatively simple joinery and a small number of pieces. Long apron boards poke out the end slightly, legs and apron overlap, etc. My favorite detail is the way the top floats slightly above the base.
